DEFINITIONS:
"Software":
All code included in this application and it's source code.

"User":
Any person(s) with a copy of this Software.

"Profits":
Any method of gaining money or other benefits from a User.

"Open-Source":
The Software's source code can be easily seen and read by any User without restrictions of any kind, including paywalls, ads, or code obfuscation.

"Malware":
Any code that gets Profits from a User or intentionally harms a User's computer or lifestyle, including viruses, adware, botnets, trackers, etc.

