A) Modify the Software for Malicious Intent, including all forms of viruses, adware, botnets, or any form of Malware;
B) Modify the Software for Profits, including adding trackers, ads, or any other way of gaining Profits from a User;
C) Redistribute or Publish the Software for Profits, including selling the Software;
D) Redistribute or Publish the Software without making it Open-Source;
E) Redistribute or Publish the Software in a way that restricts it's use, not including language barriers.